<item>
            <title>[LU-19803] kernel update [RHEL 8.10 4.18.0-553.94.1.el8_10]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19803</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: smb: client: Fix use-after-free in cifs_fill_dirent (CVE-2025-38051)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: smb: client: let recv_done verify data_offset, data_length and remaining_data_length (CVE-2025-39933)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: drm/i915: mark requests for GuC virtual engines to avoid use-after-free (CVE-2023-53552)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: drm/sched: Fix potential double free in drm_sched_job_add_resv_dependencies (CVE-2025-40096)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: net: atlantic: fix fragment overflow handling in RX path (CVE-2025-68301)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---8/x86_64/RHSA-2026:0759&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---8/x86_64/RHSA-2026:0759&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
